            <lb/>et <abbr>M.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr> le <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs type="person">Iselin</rs>, si Vous le voyez, <abbr>M.<hi rend="sup">rs</hi></abbr>
            <lb/><rs type="person">Bringolf</rs>, <rs type="person">Raillard</rs> et les autres amis co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>uns.</foreign>
        <lb/>Meinen <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1366600037 pers_DE-588-1366599853">Eltern</rs> einen grus im vorbe<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>gang.</p>
